Notes: UWO ranked 23rd in NCAA Div. III by D3hoops.com...UWO's first game since
Dec. 4...UWO's 11th straight home win...UWO's 10th straight win over RC...UWO
outscored RC, 22-4, in the second quarter...UWO got 13 points from Freitag and
12 each from Arneson and Jorgensen...UWO had 11 players score points.
